The '''bridge crystal''', also called the '''rainbow crystal''', was a magical [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] artifact. By standing at the edge of the [[Gorge of Fire]] and letting the [[Star/Legends|suns]] rays shine through the crystal, one could form a [[Rainbow Bridge]] over it. The bridge was the only passage between the forests of the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]]s and the land of [[Zandor]], although if the sun stopped shining, the rainbow would disappear. The Ewok [[Chief/Legends|Chief]] [[Chirpa/Legends|Chirpa]] of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] had stolen the crystal from the [[Ogre]] [[Gantu]] in his youth, in order to prevent Gantu from raiding Ewok lands. The crystal was later destroyed by accident in a confrontation between Gantu and the Ewok [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]].<ref name="Ewoks 1" />

